cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.NE, cs.SY. 

The paper proposes methods for improving the scalability of multi-agent reinforcement learning using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). The paper also deals with nonstationarity and conditioning, which are relevant to the categories cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
